channel.title: Exercises: Data Types :: Java Web Development
channel.description: Getting Started Work on these exercises in the IntelliJ java-web-dev-projects project. Create a new class for each numbered exercise. You may name the classes whatever you like, but use proper Java Naming Conventions and make sure that the file name matches the class name.
